        "timestamp": "2019-12-10 11:29:55.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Patch Set 1:\n> \n> Samuli, Are you suggesting all onap component artifact are moved to demo repo such as dcae monitoring , operation policy, threshold policy , data dictionary, cba, etc..?\n\nYes. E.g. I know from Policy that some demo policies (TCA and operational policies) are part of Policy git repos and even as part of production code i.e some operational policies are even activated by default for demos so that user don't need even to do normal onboarding of control loop, which is purely wrong. None of them should be there within production code that should be a generic platform.",
